BETTING WITH BOB 
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $60 Sunday when Present Value, on which 
he bet $50 to win, ran out in the eighth race, and his $10 triple "ended" when 
Shimmering Star was fourth in the sixth race. Bob, who started the meeting with 
a mythical $1,000 bankroll is now at $690. 
Bob's bet today is a $30 parlay from Hidden Garden in the third to Over The 
Pole in the fifth. 
Sunday's Bankroll: $750 
Sunday's Loss: $60 
Current Bankroll: $690 
